# Context Discipline

- Always read project context before coding:
  - `docs/PRD.md`
  - `docs/MOBILE_TECHNICAL_SPEC.md`
  - `docs/DECISIONS.md`
  - `docs/CURRENT_STATE.md`
  - `docs/TODO.md`
  - latest entries in `docs/BUILD_JOURNAL.md`
  - relevant `.cursor/rules`
  - relevant `.cursor/skills`
- Obey `docs/DECISIONS.md`.
- Do not implement outside requested scope.
- Do not build app features when the prompt only asks for documentation, planning, rules, or memory.
- After every prompt, update:
  - `docs/CURRENT_STATE.md`
  - `docs/TODO.md`
  - `docs/BUILD_JOURNAL.md`
- `docs/BUILD_JOURNAL.md` is append-only.

